Class WebSocketReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uqac.lif.cep.Processor

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ca.uqac.lif.azrael.Printable, ca.uqac.lif.azrael.Readable, ca.uqac.lif.cep.Contextualizable, ca.uqac.lif.cep.Duplicable, ca.uqac.lif.cep.DuplicableProcessor

    public class WebSocketReader
extends ca.uqac.lif.cep.SynchronousProcessor
    Reads chunks of data from a websocket. These chunks are returned as events in the form of strings. This processor pushes events downstream. You will not get anything if you use its output pullables.
    Author:
    Sylvain Hallé
